name: Mex.O1
description: Mex is the 3rd member of the Oxbot-X team. He is the strongest boy in the group. The Oxbot-X team was brought together from 3 gladiators who winning the arane battles in the great kingdom. 3 armors made by Merkars are given to this team. Mex uses bronze armor. Their aim is to assassinate the ruthless Veroun.
